  "featureInfoPOCreateStep4Title": "তৈরি করুন the order",
  "featureInfoPOCreateStep4Desc": "ট্যাপ 'Create' থেকে save the purchase order as a খসড়া.",
  "featureInfoPOManageTitle": "Managing ক্রয় অর্ডার",
  "featureInfoPOManageStep1Title": "পাঠান the order",
  "featureInfoPOManageStep1Desc": "When ready, use the 'Send' action on a খসড়া order থেকে mark it as পাঠানো হয়েছে থেকে the supplier.",
  "featureInfoPOManageStep2Title": "গ্রহণ করুন the order",
  "featureInfoPOManageStep2Desc": "When goods arrive, use the 'Receive' action on a পাঠানো হয়েছে order থেকে mark it as গৃহীত. স্টক levels update automatically.",
  "featureInfoPOManageStep3Title": "বাতিল if needed",
