  "featureInfoTransfersManageTitle": "Managing স্টক স্থানান্তর",
  "featureInfoTransfersManageStep1Title": "অনুমোদন করুন the transfer",
  "featureInfoTransfersManageStep1Desc": "ব্যবহার the 'Approve' action on মুলতুবি transfers. এই changes the status থেকে মধ্যে Transit.",
  "featureInfoTransfersManageStep2Title": "গ্রহণ করুন the transfer",
  "featureInfoTransfersManageStep2Desc": "When the goods arrive at the destination, use the 'Receive' action. স্টক levels are updated at both stores.",
  "featureInfoTransfersManageStep3Title": "বাতিল if needed",
