  "featureInfoRecipesCreateStep4Title": "যোগ করুন ingredients",
  "featureInfoRecipesCreateStep4Desc": "নির্বাচন করুন the ingredient product, enter the ingredient quantity, এবং set the waste percentage (how much material হলো typically wasted). ট্যাপ 'Create' থেকে save.",
  "featureInfoRecipesDeleteTitle": "মুছে ফেলা হচ্ছে a Recipe",
  "featureInfoRecipesDeleteStep1Title": "খুঁজুন the recipe in the table",
  "featureInfoRecipesDeleteStep1Desc": "Locate the recipe you want থেকে delete in the list showing product name, yield, এবং status.",
  "featureInfoRecipesDeleteStep2Title": "মুছুন এবং confirm",
  "featureInfoRecipesDeleteStep2Desc": "ক্লিক the 'Delete' action এবং confirm in the dialog. এই removes the recipe definition.",
  "featureInfoRecipesTip1": "সেট the waste percentage থেকে account জন্য material lost during production (e.g. trimming, evaporation).",
  "featureInfoStockLevelsTitle": "স্টক স্তর",
  "featureInfoStockLevelsDesc": "Monitor current stock quantities জন্য all products. দেখুন available এবং reserved stock, average cost, এবং reorder status. সেট reorder points এবং maximum stock levels থেকে get alerts when stock হলো low.",
